query: SELECT USU.NOMEUSU AS comprador, COUNT(DISTINCT CAB.NUNOTA) AS qtdConfirmados, SUM(CAB.VLRNOTA) AS vlrConfirmados FROM TGFCAB CAB JOIN TSIUSU USU ON USU.CODUSU = CAB.CODUSUINC JOIN TGFITE I ON I.NUNOTA = CAB.NUNOTA AND I.CODEMP = CAB.CODEMP AND I.CODPROD = 9558 WHERE CAB.TIPMOV = 'O' AND CAB.STATUSNOTA = 'L' AND CAB.DTNEG BETWEEN '2025-10-01' AND '2025-12-31' AND CAB.CODUSUINC IN (104,107,263,309) GROUP BY USU.NOMEUSU ORDER BY USU.NOMEUSU;
originalQuery: SELECT USU.NOMEUSU AS comprador, COUNT(DISTINCT CAB.NUNOTA) AS qtdConfirmados, SUM(CAB.VLRNOTA) AS vlrConfirmados FROM TGFCAB CAB JOIN TSIUSU USU ON USU.CODUSU = CAB.CODUSUINC JOIN TGFITE I ON I.NUNOTA = CAB.NUNOTA AND I.CODEMP = CAB.CODEMP AND I.CODPROD = 9558 WHERE CAB.TIPMOV = 'O' AND CAB.STATUSNOTA = 'L' AND CAB.DTNEG BETWEEN '2025-10-01' AND '2025-12-31' AND CAB.CODUSUINC IN (104,107,263,309) GROUP BY USU.NOMEUSU ORDER BY USU.NOMEUSU;
